premise_source_doc_sentence: Heinrich Luitpold Himmler  (  -LSB- ˈhaɪnʁɪç ˈluˑɪtˌpɔlt ˈhɪmlɐ -RSB- ; 7 October 1900 -- 23 May 1945  )  was Reichsführer of the Schutzstaffel  (  Protection Squadron ; SS  )  , and a leading member of the Nazi Party  (  NSDAP  )  of Germany .
